short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Integration of Google Calendar with Calendyze, for Calendyze Pro users to see meeting costs in Google Calendar events.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Calendyze extension shows your team their meeting goals right in their calendar. Set guardrails to help shape your meeting culture.
